docs.title: 颜色 Color
docs.description: 颜色是指UI界面设计中使用的色彩体系，Arco Design定义了：品牌色、中立色、功能色三部分色彩，以及衍生出的UI调色板。可用于创建反应您的品牌或风格的颜色主题。
docs.enDescription: Color refers to the color system used in UI interface design. Arco Design defines: brand color, neutral color, functional color three-part color, and the derived UI color palette. Can be used to create colors that reflect your brand or style theme.

docs.title: 边框 Border
docs.description: 边框圆角是用一段与角的两边相切的圆弧替换原来的角，圆角的大小用圆弧的半径表示，在UI布局中圆角可以提供更友好的图像体验，在设计中使用圆角可以起到样式的区分从而让用户感知到功能的区分。
docs.enDescription: The rounded corner of the border replaces the original corner with an arc tangent to both sides of the corner. The size of the rounded corner is represented by the radius of the arc. In the UI layout, rounded corners can provide a more friendly image experience. Use circles in design Corners can be used to differentiate styles and allow users to perceive functional distinctions.

docs.title: 阴影 Shadow
docs.description: 投影是UI界面设计很重要的一个元素，它能助于我们大脑区分我们看见的UI元素，让用户对于信息的理解更加简单，提高界面品质。Arco Design 提供了可定义不同深度和角度的投影值
docs.enDescription: Projection is a very important element in UI interface design. It can help our brains distinguish the UI elements we see, making it easier for users to understand information and improving the quality of the interface. Arco Design provides projection values that define different depths and angles

docs.title: 字体 Font
docs.description: 字体是UI设计中最基本的构成之一。字体系统的建立主要解决的是内容可读性以及信息的表达，同时选择不同的字体传达不同的设计风格。通过定义字体的使用规则在设计上达到统一性和整体性，从而在阅读的舒适性上达到平衡。
docs.enDescription: Fonts are one of the most basic components of UI design. The establishment of the font system mainly solves the readability of content and the expression of information, and chooses different fonts to convey different design styles. By defining the rules for the use of fonts, unity and integrity are achieved in the design, so as to achieve a balance in the comfort of reading.

docs.enDescription: In order to control the size variability in UI design, we make a minimum constraint on the actual distance of UI design, which is convenient to ensure the consistency of product styles throughout the site.
